<p class="">On a point of Order. Is it not well within the rights, privileges and responsibilities of this House to point the moral in a case like this where opportunity has been given to a newspaper of taking the proper course, where that proper course has been refused and where <span id="341" class="column-number" data-column-number="341"></span> a gross imputation has been made not only upon the Ministry of Health, but indirectly on the public administration of this country?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
