<p class="">I do not know whether the hon. Member is suggesting I was expressing an <em>ex parte</em> view. I hope I was expressing the honest and proper view of the House of Commons. I will leave it at that.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
